      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition and has been treated with the highest level of care. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, glass-like finish, and the interior is pristine, smelling like new with no signs of wear on the upholstery or carpets. Every mechanical component functions perfectly, and the car has been maintained strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership.",
