    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it's time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've babied this ride from day one, always keeping it garaged and sparkling clean. If you're looking for a dream car that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a road trip today, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it in person!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
